{"type": "article", "id": 29171, "title": "节水器", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-05T22:53:28Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 23, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160705215332F6dZk9LMnfueCsKr.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>淋浴时免不了会因为调节水温而浪费珍贵的水资源，根据统计这期间每分钟最多可能浪费 12 升的水。今天介绍的这个蓝色集水器 Aguawell 就是专门为节水而设计的，淋浴时只需要打开集水盖将它放在喷头下，等水温合适之后再关紧即可。尽管每个装置的最大容量为 6 升，中间凹槽型的设计方便它们叠加后收集更多的水，装满后每个仅重 6.5 千克。和我们之前介绍的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/26857.html\">节水手提袋</a>相比，Aguawell 不仅适用于淋浴喷头，更大的接水面可以让它在很多淋浴环境中都能起到节水的效果。这是它的<a href=\"http://aguawell.com.br/?product=aguawell\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 49 雷亚尔。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160705215515NfjUqQVur0DimBS4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.754286\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160705215516xyRidIwQzY4u9JgX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.842298\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160705215515wukrq6vp8FoQUdc7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707143\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160705215515ZuPgaS4B5RmFQjdI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.655257\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}